#
# Global CDNs
#

Globally whitelist jsDelivr CDN
    * cdn.jsdelivr.net
        * cdn.jsdelivr.net *
        * cdn.jsdelivr.net script

Globally whitelist CDNJS CDN
    * cdnjs.com
        * cdnjs.com *
        * cdnjs.com script
    * cdnjs.cloudflare.com
        * cdnjs.cloudflare.com *
        * cdnjs.cloudflare.com script

Globally whitelist Google CDN
    * ajax.googleapis.com
        * ajax.googleapis.com *
        * ajax.googleapis.com script

Globally whitelist Microsoft CDN
    * ajax.aspnetcdn.com
        * ajax.aspnetcdn.com *
        * ajax.aspnetcdn.com script

Globally whitelist jQuery CDN
    * code.jquery.com
        * code.jquery.com *
        * code.jquery.com script

Globally whitelist Fastly CDN
    * ssl.fastly.net
        * ssl.fastly.net *
        * ssl.fastly.net script

Globally whitelist UNPKG CDN
    * unpkg.com
        * unpkg.com *
        * unpkg.com script

Globally whitelist Bootstrap MaxCDN
    * maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com
        * maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com *
        * maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com script
